        "text": "Memory Index Compaction (PR #32)",
        "level": "h3"
      }
    },
    "text-pr32-full": {
      "type": "Text",
      "props": {
        "text": "Self-improve caught MEMORY.md bloating to 76KB/31K tokens — past the Read tool limit. Filed a PR that compresses it to 9.4KB (-87%) and adds per-row character caps to memory-flush so it can't recur.",
        "variant": "body"
      }
    },
